# CachyOS WSL Root Filesystem Package List
#
# This file defines the packages to install in the rootfs.
# Keep it minimal - users can install additional packages later.

# Base System
# The 'base' meta-package provides essential system utilities
base

# CachyOS Core Packages
# These provide CachyOS-specific functionality and repository access
cachyos-hooks
cachyos-keyring
cachyos-mirrorlist

# ALHP (Arch Linux Holo Ports) Packages
# Additional optimized package repositories for x86-64-v3 and higher
# Note: ALHP packages not available in standard CachyOS repositories
# Users can manually add ALHP repository after installation if desired
# alhp-keyring
# alhp-mirrorlist

# Privilege Escalation
# Required for users to perform administrative tasks
sudo

# Networking
# iptables-nft provides modern netfilter functionality
iptables-nft

# Text Editor
# Essential for configuration file editing
nano
vim

# Development Tools (optional but useful)
# Uncomment if you want basic development tools in the base image
# base-devel
# git

# Package Management Helpers
# Uncomment if you want reflector for mirror management
# reflector
